<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Required - Employee Activation</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h1 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-top: 0;">Payment Required - Employee Activation</h1>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p>Dear <%= employerName %>,</p>

        <p>Congratulations! <strong><%= candidateName %></strong> has accepted your employment offer for the position of <strong><%= jobTitle %></strong>.</p>

        <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold;">‚ö†Ô∏è Action Required: Complete Payment to Unlock Candidate Contact</p>
        </div>

        <p>To access the candidate's full contact details and proceed with onboarding, please complete the agency commission payment.</p>

        <h3 style="color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0; padding-bottom: 10px;">Payment Breakdown</h3>
        
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
            <tr style="background-color: #f8f9fa;">
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><strong>Candidate</strong></td>
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><%= candidateName %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><strong>Position</strong></td>
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><%= jobTitle %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background-color: #f8f9fa;">
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><strong>Base Compensation</strong></td>
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><%= currency %> <%= baseAmount %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><strong>Commission Rate</strong></td>
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><%= commissionRate %>%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background-color: #f8f9fa;">
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><strong>Commission Amount</strong></td>
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><%= currency %> <%= commissionAmount %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><strong>VAT (7.5%)</strong></td>
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><%= currency %> <%= vatAmount %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background-color: #e8f5e9;">
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;"><strong>Total Amount Due</strong></td>
                <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold; color: #2e7d32;"><%= currency %> <%= totalAmount %></td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= paymentUrl %>" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 15px 40px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
                Complete Payment Now
            </a>
        </div>

        <h3 style="color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0; padding-bottom: 10px;">What Happens Next?</h3>
        
        <ol style="line-height: 2;">
            <li>Click the button above to securely complete your payment via Paystack</li>
            <li>Once payment is confirmed, you'll immediately gain access to the candidate's contact details</li>
            <li>An employment contract will be automatically generated for both parties to review and sign</li>
            <li>You can then proceed with onboarding and finalize the employment arrangement</li>
        </ol>

        <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #2196F3; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>üí° Note:</strong> The candidate's personal contact information (email and phone number) will remain masked until payment is successfully completed.</p>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
        <strong>JobStack Talent Solutions Team</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
            This is an automated email from JobStack Talent Solutions.<br>
            Payment Reference: <%= paymentReference %>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
